as not shown her best in recent runs but arrives here with 5 weeks between runs. She benefits from a 3kg claim, and with a couple of subtle gear changes, she can show some decent form again. 7. CARDI BEE is in peak fitness, and she comes here off a soft win on heavy ground at Pakenham. The margin may have been boosted by the conditions, but she still put them away with authority, and she can hold her form now. Each-way. 9. MOVE THE TORANA has raced her way into some good form, and 1600m will suit her.  Her stable is running hot, and another honest effort can be expected.\",\"runners\":[1,3,7,9],\"exclusive\":true}","ratings":[{"ratingType":"Rating","ratingRunnerNumbers":[3,7,1,6]},{"ratingType":"Last12Months","ratingRunnerNumbers":[1,3,10,5]},{"ratingType":"Recent","ratingRunnerNumbers":[6,9,5,3]},{"ratingType":"Distance","ratingRunnerNumbers":[3,2,5,10]},{"ratingType":"Class","ratingRunnerNumbers":[5,9,3,6]},{"ratingType":"Time","ratingRunnerNumbers":[1,3,5,6]},{"ratingType":"Overall","ratingRunnerNumbers":[3,5,1,6]}],"multiLegApproximates":[],"betTypes":[{"wageringProduct":"Win","firstLeg":{"raceNumber":3,"venueMnemonic":"SAN","raceType":"R"}},{"wageringProduct":"Place","firstLeg":{"raceNumber":3,"venueMnemonic":"SAN","raceType":"R"}},{"wageringProduct":"Quinella","firstLeg":{"raceNumber":3,"venueMnemonic":"SAN","raceType":"R"}},{"wageringProduct":"Exacta","firstLeg":{"raceNumber":3,"venueMnemonic":"SAN","raceType":"R"}},{"wageringProduct":"Duet","firstLeg":{"raceNumber":3,"venueMnemonic":"SAN","raceType":"R"}},{"wageringProduct":"Trifecta","firstLeg":{"raceNumber":3,"venueMnemonic":"SAN","raceType":"R"}},{"wageringProduct":"FirstFour","firstLeg":{"raceNumber":3,"venueMnemonic":"SAN","raceType":"R"}},{"wageringProduct":"RunningDouble","firstLeg":{"raceNumber":3,"venueMnemonic":"SAN","raceType":"R"}},{"wageringProduct":"EarlyQuaddie","firstLeg":{"raceNumber":1,"venueMnemonic":"SAN","raceType":"R"}}]}}}